本科單單是現存物種就已經有超過200個物種，而化石物種的數量更多<ref name="wsu">{{cite web |url=http://shells.tricity.wsu.edu/ArcherdShellCollection/Bivalvia/Cardiidae.html |title=Cardiidae (Cockles) |publisher=Shells.tricity.wsu.edu |accessdate=2012-10-13 |language=en |archive-date=2012-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120304223538/http://shells.tricity.wsu.edu/ArcherdShellCollection/Bivalvia/Cardiidae.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。所以一般都會根據Vaught (1989) 的分類，將鳥尾蛤科分為五個亞科。這五個亞科分別如下{{r|shell_100158|Xu 2012|WoRMS_229}}：
